48
00:03:04,947 --> 00:03:08,567
Like if we turn this face, this orange centerpiece will stay absolutely still,

49
00:03:09,407 --> 00:03:10,288
these pieces will move,

50
00:03:10,708 --> 00:03:13,168
and then these pieces all around the edge will stay still.

51
00:03:13,848 --> 00:03:17,489
