00:06:38,365 --> 00:06:40,945
and let go and move your hands, because that's the slowest thing you can do when you're

121
00:06:40,965 --> 00:06:41,725
manipulating the cube.

122
00:06:42,108 --> 00:06:43,329
is to turn it around in your hands.

123
00:06:43,709 --> 00:06:45,390
Try and get your hand on the top to turn the top.

124
00:06:45,971 --> 00:06:48,012
So, speedcubers use their fingers and their thumbs

125
00:06:48,132 --> 00:06:51,014
and every digit to manipulate the cube on all the faces

126
00:06:51,054 --> 00:06:52,015
without having to re-grip.

127
00:06:53,056 --> 00:06:55,438
And again, practice, muscle memory, repetition.

128
00:06:56,779 --> 00:06:58,880
And we're aiming to reach this point of ultimacity

